quran[7]{c,v,t}:
  9,14,un se ( khoob ) laro. khuda un ko tumahray hathon se azaab mein daaley ga aur ruswa kere ga aur tum ko un par ghalba day ga aur momin logon ke seenon ko Shifa bakhshay ga
  9,15,aur un ke dilon se gussa daur kere ga aur jis par chahay ga rehmat kere ga. aur khuda sab kuch jaanta ( aur ) hikmat wala hai
  9,16,kiya tum log yeh khayaal karte ho ke ( be azmaish ) chore diye jao ge aur abhi khuda ne aisay logon ko mutamayyaz kiya hi nahi jinhon ne tum mein se jehaad kiye aur khuda aur is ke rasool aur mominon ke siwa kisi ko dili dost nahi banaya. aur khuda tumahray sab kamon se waaqif hai
  9,17,mushrikon ki zaiba nahi ke khuda ki masjidoon ko abad karen jab ke woh apne aap par kufar ki gawahi day rahay hain. un logon ke sab aamaal be car hain aur yeh hamesha dozakh mein rahen ge
  9,18,khuda ki masjidoon ko to woh log abad karte hain jo khuda par aur roz qayamat par imaan laatay hain aur namaz parhte aur زکواة dete hain aur khuda ke siwa kisi se nahi drtay. yahi log umeed hai ke hadaayat Yafta logon mein ( daakhil ) hon
  9,19,kiya tum ne hajion ko pani pilana aur masjid mohtaram yani ( Khana kaaba ) ko abad karna is shakhs ke aamaal jaissa khayaalkiya hai jo khuda aur roz akhirat par imaan rakhta hai aur khuda ki raah mein jehaad karta hai. yeh log khuda ke nazdeek barabar nahi hain. aur khuda zalim logon ko hadaayat nahi diya karta
  9,20,jo log imaan laaye aur watan chore gay aur khuda ki raah mein maal aur jaan se jehaad karte rahay. khuda ke haan un ke darjay bohat barray hain. aur wohi morad ko pounchanay walay hain
